title: EYL #133 Cordae on Investing, Entrepreneurship, & Music
itunes:title: EYL #133 Cordae on Investing, Entrepreneurship, & Music
description:
In episode #133, we had the privilege of sitting down with the youngest in charge. Cordae is easily one of the hottest and most talented artists of this generation. He’s a Grammy nominated artist and just dropped a highly praised project “Just Until”. 


The 23-year-old superstar doesn’t do too many interviews, but he has a lot to talk about! Aside from being a prodigy in music, Cordae is a highly skilled investor with an extremely impressive stock portfolio. He’s an entrepreneur with several successful companies including his clothing line and record label “Hi Level”, he’s a real estate investor, and a very astute businessman when it comes to music. 


In EYL 133, we talked with the young legend about all the above and more. He gave us insight into his ascension in the music game, and how he turned his talent into a booming business operation that employs his friends and family. #Cordae #music #investing
